<p>This is a remake of <a href="https://github.com/julescarbon/sortpixels.js">julescarbon's</a> port of @kimasendorf's Sort Pixels script from Processing to Javascript.</p>

<ul>original source:
     <li><a href="http://kimasendorf.com/data/ASDFPixelSort.zip">http://kimasendorf.com/data/ASDFPixelSort.zip</a></li>
</ul>

<ul>
Added:
	<li>Whole new layout/ look</li>
	<li>Ability to sort vertically
	<li>Download images</li>
	<li>Handle large file sizes</li>
	<li>Gallery of images</li>
</ul>

<ul>
Removed:
	 <li>iterations (no effect on the image)</li>
</ul>

<ul>
Contribute:
     <li>I'd love to see your artwork! Add your image into the folder img/gallery and create a pull request to get your pixel sorted art featured on the site.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
Updates:
     <li>Add ability to buy prints of pictures.</li>
     <li>Add different glitch effects.</li>
     <li>Add setting sliders with dat.gui?</li>
</ul>
